description: Citizen Pops is home to some of the best frozen yogurt and frozen popsicles in the triangle area! Their frozen yogurt, made using liquid nitrogen, is smooth and creamy. In addition, their handmade popsicles are made with 100% natural ingredients like fresh fruits, making them vegan friendly and gluten free! In the mood for a drink? Try their bubble tea which can be made over ice or blended like a shake!
name: Citizen Pops
